S

SignatureCallback - Interface in com.aheaditec.apdu.callbacks
This callback is used with ApduProvider.signData(ContainerBasic, byte[], AlgorithmID, SignatureCallback) method to get signature in form of byte array.
SignatureContinueCallback - Interface in com.aheaditec.apdu.callbacks
This callback is used only with SignatureCallback.onVerificationNeeded(VerifyCodes, SignatureContinueCallback) when the verification is required.
signData(ContainerBasic, byte[], AlgorithmID, SignatureCallback) - Method in class com.aheaditec.apdu.ApduProvider
This method signs data given by the user to the card, with specified container which holds private key, specified algorithm from AlgorithmID enum.
StatusWord - Enum in com.aheaditec.apdu.enums
This enum represents all needed SW according to standard ISO7816
